If you’d like to learn more about Sacs and Sactionals, feel free to stop by your local Showroom, schedule an appointment, shop online, or chat directly with an associate using the button in the bottom right corner of this page.

At Lovesac, we're committed to making your home as comfortable as possible. That’s why Sacs and Sactionals are specially designed to be washable, changeable, and guaranteed to last a lifetime. We believe your furniture is something you can continue to invest in, expand, and evolve over time so that it continues to meet your needs, rather than having to add it to the landfill. This helps reduce stress while freeing you to live the life you love.

Our Omaha, Nebraska showroom is home to The World’s Most Adaptable Couch™ and The World's Most Comfortable Seat™. Our associates are excited to speak with you about our latest offers, sales, and financing options. Remember, every order comes with free contactless delivery and our risk-free 60-Day Home Trial.

Whether you're looking for a sectional couch, bean bag chair, outdoor furniture, or even just an ottoman, our Omaha area showroom has something to fit your needs.
